data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Nestled in the heart of Ocala, this charming property at 129 SE 31st Ave offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. This single-family home features three spacious bedrooms and two updated bathrooms and boasts a spacious 1,832 square foot layout. The well-maintained interior is flooded with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The home has an extra large inside laundry room with tons of additional storage space. Step outside to the shaded deck area, where you can enjoy the Florida sunshine and create your own oasis. You are walking distance to tennis courts, Veterans park, golf course and minutes from downtown Ocala. The roof was done in 2018, HVAC in 2017, gas hot water heater and gas stove were replaced in 2022. New camera system conveys with the home. Don’t miss the opportunity to make this property your new home. Schedule a showing today to experience all that this home has to offer.
